---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
import RecentPublications from "../components/RecentPublications.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body class="w-full max-w-screen-md mx-auto my-4 bg-sage-100 dark:bg-sage-900 dark:text-sage-100 transition-colors duration-300" >
    <Header />
    <main class="flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="px-4 md:px-16 flex flex-col gap-4 md:my-10">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl w-full">It Works on My Blog!</h1>
        <p class="w-full text-justify text-base md:text-lg">
          Hey there, fellow code wrangler! 👨‍💻👩‍💻 If you’ve ever stared at a bug for hours, only to realize you forgot a semicolon, or deployed something that worked perfectly on localhost but turned into a dumpster fire in production, well then congratulations, you’re in the right place! 🎉
        </p>
        
         <p class="w-full text-justify text-base md:text-lg">
          Expect deep dives into tech, some questionable analogies, and the occasional existential crisis about why <i>null</i> even exists. Oh, and if you don’t laugh at least once per blog post, I’ll personally refund your reading time (terms and conditions apply, aka: I won’t).
        </p>
        <p class="w-full text-justify text-base md:text-lg">
          So grab a coffee, brace yourself for some top-tier tech ramblings, and remember: <strong style = 'color:#819a91'>if it works on your machine, it probably won't work anywhere else.</strong> 💁
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center gap-2.5 px-4 lg:px-0 mt-6">
        <img
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/31206896/pexels-photo-31206896.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&lazy=load"
          alt="Astronaut"
        />
        <p class="italic text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          Photo by <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/akshatsonic/"
            >Myself :hehe:</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
	  <RecentPublications />
	      </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

